data.description: Nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac within Lake Francis Estates, this charming home exudes serenity. Recently updated, the home showcases freshly painted interiors and exteriors. The kitchen features revamped cabinets, new butcher block countertops with complimentary backsplash, new kitchen sink & faucet, microwave, and stove. New LVP flooring installed throughout the living, dining, and master bedroom, complemented by fresh carpet in the additional bedrooms. The living room's lofty ceiling and wood burning fireplace create a warm ambiance for comfort. Easily access the spacious screened back porch from either the master bedroom or the dining room. From there, you'll enjoy views of the generously sized fenced backyard, creating the perfect setting for relaxation and outdoor enjoyment. You will appreciate the convenience of its proximity to Navy Federal, shopping, beaches, and easy access to I-10.
